                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10178" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">PJMT-0167</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">241 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“借鸡生蛋”壮发展、“合作共赢”奔富路： 文丰羊肚菌专业种植合作社发展之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">&quot;Leveraging external Resources to Foster Growth, and Collaborating for Mutual Prosperity&quot;: The Developmental Pathway of Wenfeng Morchella Professional Cultivation Cooperative</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王永强，张苓煜，杨开欣，朱玉春，刘天军，岑欣蕊，刘国欣</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西北农林科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">麟游县常乐文丰食用菌种植专业合作社</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农林牧副渔业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">项目评价；社企联合；羊肚菌合作社</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Project evaluation; Cooperation between Famer Cooperative and agro-enterprise; Morchella Cooperative</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陕西省宝鸡市麟游县的文丰羊肚菌专业合作社，自其诞生之日起便承载着带动农民增收致富的厚望。合作社的初衷是利用羊肚菌这一高价值经济作物，为社员们开辟一条致富之路。然而，合作社在推进羊肚菌种植项目的过程中，并非一帆风顺，而是经历了不少波折与挑战。本案例以合作社羊肚菌种植项目的发展历程作为主线展开描述，详细讲述了文丰羊肚菌专业种植合作社在羊肚菌种植发展过程中面临的问题和最终寻求突破的方式。首先，介绍了合作社的组建过程；其次，介绍了合作社亟需扩张种植规模，选择“借鸡生蛋”，借用世界银行资金完成生产规模的扩大；再次，介绍了合作社由于技术掌握不精、资金入不敷出等问题陷入困境，致使合作社发展陷入低迷状态；最后，介绍了合作社在政府帮助下，吸引社会资本、盘活合作社资产，最终通过与企业合作实现互利共赢。本案例旨在引导学习者站在合作社项目发展视角下，借助项目评估，企业价值等相关理论知识、方法和工具，从合作社项目发展的全过程思考如何进行项目评估与优化，期望可以提供一些启示。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Since its establishment, the Wenfeng Morchella Professional Cooperative in Linyou County, Baoji City, Shaanxi Province, has been tasked with the significant mission of boosting farmers&#39; income and promoting rural prosperity. The cooperative&#39;s original intention was to leverage morchella—a high-value economic crop—to open up a path to wealth for its members. However, the process of advancing the morchella cultivation project was far from smooth, marked by numerous twists and challenges. This case study unfolds along the main thread of the cooperative&#39;s project development, detailing the problems encountered in morchella cultivation and the strategies employed to overcome them.
First, it introduces the cooperative&#39;s formation process, highlighting the initial organizational framework and collaborative mechanisms established to aggregate rural resources. Second, as the cooperative urgently needed to expand its cultivation scale, it adopted a strategy of &quot;borrowing chickens to lay eggs&quot;—securing funds from the World Bank to complete production scale expansion, demonstrating proactive utilization of external financial resources. Third, the narrative addresses the cooperative&#39;s predicament caused by inadequate technical mastery and financial shortfalls, which led to a prolonged stagnation in development as costs exceeded revenues and operational inefficiencies emerged. Finally, it describes how, with government support, the cooperative attracted social capital, revitalized its assets, and ultimately achieved mutual benefit through partnerships with enterprises, marking a turning point toward sustainable development.
This case aims to guide learners to analyze project evaluation and optimization from the holistic perspective of cooperative project development. By applying relevant theoretical knowledge, methods, and tools such as project assessment and corporate value analysis, learners are encouraged to reflect on critical success factors, risk management, and strategic adjustments throughout the project lifecycle, with the expectation of providing practical insights for similar agricultural cooperatives.
</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《项目评估与管理》、《项目评价与管理》、《农业投资项目评估与管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">项目评估的核心维度;项目风险管理;农企合作模式;农业项目的社会效益评估</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-12</td>
                            </tr>
